id":20317,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T10:49:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T12:40:04.000Z","msg":"有幾撚可憐？"},{"pid":"f02a3a2105c90c07f19d4787ccfaca0aea979edf","tid":2269622,"uid":278152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T12:41:52.000Z","msg":"咁做多年警察，連結婚的錢都存唔到？<br />\n我就真係唔撚信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結婚呢家野，有錢大搞，無錢都可以細搞，<br />\n完全係自己拎黎囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家破產仲唔洗還錢，停職仲有人工出，on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話唔定到時警隊復埋佢職添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}